\title{basic macros}

\xmlns:html{http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml}

\def\hr{
  \<html:hr>{}
}
\def\nowrap[body]{\<html:span>[style]{white-space: nowrap}{\body}}
\def\color[colorcode][body]{
  \<html:span>[style]{color:\colorcode}{\body}
}

\p{This tree defines the basic notational macros used across my forest. Deriving from jsm-trees.}
